data.description: Great ranch style plan with bonus upstairs that could be used as 4th bedroom. Open concept living with laminate hardwood flooring, vaulted ceilings, stone accented fireplace and plenty of natural light. Kitchen features tons of granite counter space & storage, tile backsplash, butler's pantry and stainless steel appliances. Master en-suite with dual vanities, soaking tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. Garage has been converted to climate controlled living space with a separate workshop within. Could be used as a recreation or bonus room or any type of flex space. Could be converted back if buyer wants a garage. Large screened porch and patio opens to a backyard oasis! Flat, fenced-in rear lot with fire pit area, pool, pool deck and pool house or entertaining area. House has been freshly painted. No HOA.
